Mozilla,Persona,is,an,online,identity,service,for,websites,and,web,applications,Users,can,set,how,they,would,like,to,login,to,websites,and,applications,Publishers,can,add,Persona,to,their,websites,and,applications,The,Mozilla,Persona,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Persona,with,other,applications,and,websites,The,main,API,methods,include,logging,in,to,websites,and,verifying,identities